title: Ground News - The crisis had to come, now we have risen, David Kaše praised | Českénoviny.cz
text:
Summary by ceskenoviny.cz Hradec Králové - Three wins from the last four games, five points in a row or eleven goals scored in three days. These are statistics indicating that hockey's Litvinov is returning to the saddle again after a crisis period. “We are showing good performances,” striker David Kaše praised himself when talking to journalists after today's successful performance of the North Bohemians in Hradec Králové.
